The '''Brazilian Cultural Center''' ({{lang-pt|Centro Cultural Brasileiro}}, abbreviated '''CCB''') is an institution subordinated to the Brazilian diplomatic missions in each country, being the main instrument for the execution of the Brazilian cultural policy abroad.<ref>[http://www.plusnews.org/pt/Report.aspx?ReportId=81074 São Tomé e Príncipe: Campanha com jeito de espetáculo, PlusNews news]</ref><ref>[http://www.agencialusa.com.br/index.php?iden=818 Moçambicano assume centro cultural brasileiro em Maputo, Agência Lusa news]{{dead link|date=November 2016 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>
Formerly it was known as the '''Center of Brazilian Studies''' or '''Center for Brazilian Studies''' (''Centro de Estudos Brasileiros''),<ref>[http://www.dc.mre.gov.br/box-02/lima-centro-cultural-brasil-peru dc.mre.gov.br] {{webarchive |url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110719224903/http://www.dc.mre.gov.br/box-02/lima-centro-cultural-brasil-peru |date=July 19, 2011 }}</ref>
There are Brazilian Cultural Centers currently in [[Angola]], [[Bolivia]], [[Cape Verde]], [[Chile]], [[Colombia]], [[Costa Rica]], [[Dominican Republic]], [[Ecuador]], [[El Salvador]], [[Finland]], [[Germany]], [[Guinea Bissau]], [[Guyana]], [[Haiti]], [[Italy]], [[Lebanon]], [[Mexico]], [[Mozambique]], [[Nicaragua]], [[Panama]], [[Paraguay]], [[Peru]], [[São Tomé and Príncipe]], [[South Africa]], [[Spain]], [[Suriname]], the [[United States]], [[Uruguay]] and [[Venezuela]].<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.dc.mre.gov.br/lingua-e-literatura/centros-culturais-do-brasil# |title=Brazilian Cultural Centers directions, Brazilian Ministry of Foreign Affairs website |access-date=2010-04-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100818161008/http://www.dc.mre.gov.br/lingua-e-literatura/centros-culturais-do-brasil# |archive-date=2010-08-18 |dead-url=yes |df= }}</ref><ref>[http://www.ceb-barcelona.org/os_outros_cebs.htm Brazilian Cultural Centers directions, Brazilian Cultural Center Barcelona website] {{webarchive |url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100802025856/http://www.ceb-barcelona.org/os_outros_cebs.htm |date=August 2, 2010 }}</ref>
The centers are also home to the [[CELPE-Bras]] exams.<ref>[http://www.inep.gov.br/download/celpebras/2010/Postos_de_aplicacao.pdf Authorized institutions for the application of CELPE-Bras exams, as of 2010]</ref>
