* ''[[:fa:نفس (مجموعه تلویزیونی)|Nafas]]'' ({{lang-fa|نفس}}): 2017 drama series directed by Jalil Saman features 1970s.<ref name="Saman" /><ref>{{citation|title=Iran TV uses green screen to bypass headscarf rules|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/wires/afp/article-4558258/Iran-TV-uses-green-screen-bypass-headscarf-rules.html|publisher=[[Mail Online]]|date=31 May 2017|access-date=13 June 2017}}</ref>

